            <p class="description">
                Your safety matters to us. Please add emergency contact numbers so we can share your location during critical situations.
            </p>
            
            <div class="btn-container d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
                <a href="/home" class="custom-btn btn-secondary-custom">
                    <span style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">Maybe Later</span>
